##------- WEB -------##

# firefox
super + alt + f
	firefox

# lightcord
super + alt + l
	lightcord

##------- DEV -------##

# vscode
super + alt + c
	code

##------- SETTINGS -------##

# wallpaper
super + alt + w
    bspc rule -a \* -o state=floating && nitrogen

